summary: An Ordinance relating to books, papers and other property belonging to the City of Seattle, and books, records, accounts, statements, abstracts, returns, reports, papers, plats, profiles, maps, charts, plans, specifications, estimates, drawings or other written or printed data made or kept by any city official or other person in the employ of the city, or which shall be produced or procured by the labor of any one while in the service of the city, and providing a penalty for the violation thereof.
